        {
            "title": "黑期高水逾400點 重磅港股ADR幾全升 京東ADR逆市跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場繼續憧憬環球關稅戰似緩和，外圍股市再度反彈。新加坡黑期於今早約8時10分亦升427點或2.04%，報21341點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報21097點，較香港上日現貨收市高182點或0.87%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣445.1元，較上日香港收市高1.74元或0.39%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣104.4元，較上日香港收市高1.43元或1.39%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣145元，較上日香港收市高1.52元或1.06%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣141.2元，較上日香港收市低1.88元或1.31%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣44.9元，較上日香港收市高0.62元或1.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣77.4元，較上日香港收市高1.88元或2.49%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣50.7元，較上日香港收市高0.59元或1.17%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣317.9元，較上日香港收市高5.48元或1.75%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣42.8元，較上日香港收市高0.2元或0.46%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣6.5元，較上日香港收市高0.06元或0.87%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報21059點，升203點，較上日恒指收市20914點，高水144點。科指期貨夜市收報4940點，較上日科指收市高水40點；國指期貨夜市收報7860點，較上日國指收市高水58點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852185-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%b9%be%e5%85%a8%e5%8d%87-%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1adr%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c",
