        {
            "title": "英股升逾0.6%　法德股市低收0.3%至近1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14848591&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市3大指數個別發展。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.1%，報486點，盤中最多曾挫1.59%。工業用品股及油氣股都下挫逾1.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報7964點，升50點，升幅0.64%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報7104點，跌21點，跌幅0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報20374點，跌188點，跌幅0.92%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報34027點，下降0.73%或249點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報12286點，下跌0.18%或21點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14848591-%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be0-6%e3%80%80%e6%b3%95%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b60-3%e8%87%b3%e8%bf%911-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094813_20191028_EuropeStock_AP_source-ap_-1-1-1-1-1-2-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 08:15:53",
